{"type": "article", "id": 26985, "title": "马云不会参会国际反假联盟，以及，Free People 婚纱不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-18T12:14:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27781, "name": "时尚网站"}, {"id": 1395, "name": "婚纱"}, {"id": 14917, "name": "秋季"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 11165, "name": "夏日"}, {"id": 13416, "name": "凉鞋"}, {"id": 5142, "name": "网购"}, {"id": 18474, "name": "Free people"}, {"id": 1922, "name": "Celine"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 27782, "name": "Rue La La"}, {"id": 5228, "name": "UGG"}, {"id": 4058, "name": "Target"}, {"id": 20048, "name": "Nordstrom"}, {"id": 27783, "name": "Stylecaster"}, {"id": 1515, "name": "马云"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132949eWE2LXipkjQq1PIA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Target-hires-Nordstrom-exec-as-chief-merchandising-officer,693733.html\"><b>Target 聘用 Nordstrom 前高管担任首席营销官</b></a>｜美国知名百货公司 Target  日前宣布将聘用美国另一百货公司前高管 Mark Tritton 担任首席营销官，接替一年前从这一职位上离开的 Kathryn Tesija，Mark 此前担任 Nordstrom 的总裁职位，并在 Timberland 和 Nike 工作过。同时宣布 Jason Goldberger  晋升担任首席数字官。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Rue-La-La-appoints-new-Chief-Executive-Officer,693785.html\"><b>Rue La La 任命新 CEO</b></a>｜折扣网站 Rue La La 周二宣布将由 Mark McWeeny  担任新首席执政官，接替在这一职位上已有 16 年的 Steve Davis，McWeeny 是 Rue La La 联合创始人之一，此前在集团担任过首席财政官及首席市场官。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Stylecaster-relaunch-results-in-nearly-100-percent-brand-growth,693765.html\"><b>Stylecaster 改版后访客量大增</b></a>｜纽约时尚网站 Stylecaster  2016 年 1 月改版重启，logo、网站设计、购物板块、公司使命及移动端体验都有所调整，每月独立访客达到 470 万，与 2015 年 6 月相比增长了 92%。社交媒体上的粉丝也有 115% 的增长，还被有“互联网的奥斯卡”之称的 Webby 大奖提名最佳时尚、美妆网站。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/technology/alibaba-jack-ma-iacc-10432466/\"><b>马云将不会出席 IACC 大会</b></a>｜国际反伪联盟 （IACC）继宣布阿里巴巴创始人马云将于 5 月 18－5 月 20 日在其春季大会上作为主讲嘉宾发言，过去两周失去了三个主要品牌 Michael Kors、Gucci 和 Tiffany &amp; Co.，并面临更多舆论压力，5 月 14 日宣布暂停阿里巴巴的会员资格，周二又宣布马云将不会出席 IACC 大会。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">波西米亚风的 Free People 近年来热度不减，每次新品上市都令人期待，最近又发布了<a href=\"http://popbee.com/wedding/ffree-people-wedding-dresses-2016-shop/\">最新一季婚纱的 lookbook</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132931gzJibow3IXuPF9Ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132931tmNpbCTiZxvSJDfs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329324hAdxiyqTQB0RPlC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132932mZ8IswnMRb5XyYFt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213293306lfUynKX4csbwiF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132933oKPaZX3gRciFwGvT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021329336qBxakOVyr74fgEs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">TOM FORD 推出 <a href=\"http://popbee.com/beauty/make-up/tom-ford-beauty-summer-2016-soleil-collection/\">2016 夏季 Soleil 系列彩妆</a>，棕色系为主，白色和金色的外包装，其中细长白管口红采用了夹心设计。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132934bZMmx5pS4ksJeQ3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6484375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132934BZKoEpjmO3vg27UD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132935TUcmYqN5jgFp70OK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">台北复合品牌精品店 Hotel V  拍摄了名为<a href=\"http://www.everydayobject.us/2016/05/16/cruise-the-city-by-hotel-v/\">“ CRUISE THE CITY”的夏日男女装特辑</a>，看起来很清新：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213293542sdC1J3yZVUh6oF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132936DaF85Y9Jr2Qw014j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132936gc3W61ILquKtTlaV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213293759r7hQsVGT0OZjpD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132938If2h4CcmElbZ0tve.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132938IvDPY1bjFXRmK62Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132938GKLZ79P5AgX1hBl8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132939kbwp56yKI3xt9ovW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.celine.com/zh_cn/collections/fall/handbags\">Celine 2016 年秋款包袋上市</a>，点击下划线查看全系列：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images me